      "summary": "Discover how Adani Realty used Click-to-WhatsApp Ads and AiSensy to improve lead quality, reduce acquisition costs, and increase qualified buyer intent at scale.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nReal Estate\nProducts / Services\nResidential Projects, Luxury Homes, Commercial Developments\nWebsite\nhttps://adanirealty.com/\nLow-Intent Leads from Traditional Campaigns\nA large share of incoming leads lacked immediate purchase intent, making it harder for the sales team to prioritize serious buyers and improve conversion rates.\nHigh Drop-Off on Conventional Landing Pages\nUsers coming from paid campaigns often dropped off before completing lead forms, reducing the number of qualified leads generated from ad spend.\nLonger Time to Site Visit Conversion\nThe gap between initial inquiry and actual site visit was too long, slowing down the sales cycle and increasing acquisition inefficiencies.\nClick-to-WhatsApp Ads for Instant Buyer Engagement\nInstead of sending users to a traditional landing page, Adani Realty used\nMeta Click-to-WhatsApp Ads\nto start conversations instantly with interested prospects.\nThis helped:\nReduce form abandonment\nCapture buyer intent in real time\nImprove the speed of initial engagement\nBy removing unnecessary steps, prospects could express interest faster and more naturally through WhatsApp.\nLearn More\nAutomated Lead Qualification on WhatsApp\nAiSensy helped Adani Realty streamline the early-stage qualification journey through conversational automation.\nPotential buyers could be guided through:\nProject interest selection\nBudget qualification\nLocation preference\nSite visit intent\nLead capture details\nThis allowed the team to identify\nsales-qualified leads faster\nand reduce time wasted on low-intent inquiries.\nLearn More\nFaster Follow-Ups and Higher Intent Conversations\nWith WhatsApp as the primary engagement channel, Adani Realty could continue conversations in a familiar, high-response environment.\nThis made it easier to:\nRe-engage interested buyers\nShare project details instantly\nNurture warm leads faster\nImprove coordination for site visits\nThe result was a smoother buyer journey with stronger intent signals from the start.\nCentralized Campaign and Lead Management\nWith AiSensy, Adani Realty was able to manage campaign-driven WhatsApp conversations in one centralized platform.\nThis enabled the team to:\nTrack responses more efficiently\nHandle inbound buyer conversations faster\nStandardize communication across campaigns\nImprove overall lead handling workflows\n30% Reduction in Cost Per Lead\nBy replacing friction-heavy landing page flows with direct WhatsApp conversations, Adani Realty significantly improved campaign efficiency and reduced CPL.\n25% Lower Cost Per Qualified Lead\nConversational lead qualification helped the team identify serious buyers faster, reducing the cost of acquiring genuinely sales-ready prospects.\n30% Growth in Sales-Qualified Leads\nWith faster engagement and better lead filtering, Adani Realty increased the volume of high-intent, sales-qualified leads entering the funnel.\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and ot",
