      "summary": "Find out how Cosco, one of the most renowned Sporting equipment across the globe used AiSensy to drive 3x more reach & conversions.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nSports Goods Manufacturing and Retail\nHeadquarters\nNew Delhi, India\nCompany Size\n455 Employees\nProducts\nA wide range of sports and fitness equipment\nLearn More\nPoor reach\nWith emails & WhatsApp Business app, Cosco was only able to penetrate 35% of it's audience.\nDelay in Responses with Emails\nCosco used to send the latest updates & offers via emails but did not get enough responses quickly.\nLimited Broadcasting Capability\nThe major limitation of using WhatsApp Business App for Broadcasting was the 256 people Broadcast limit.\nBroadcast Offers to Unlimited Users in One Go\nUsing AiSensy’s platform, Cosco achieved:\n• Seamless message delivery to its entire customer base\n, even to those who hadn’t saved its contact number.\n•\nCompliance with\nWhatsApp’s best practices\n, ensuring high deliverability without the risk of being blocked.\n• Outstanding results:\nA\n98% message open rate\n, enabling faster and wider customer engagement.\nLearn More\nTime-Saving Automation for Maximum Efficiency\nCosco automated key notifications on WhatsApp, such as:\n•\nOrder confirmations\n•\nDelivery updates\n•\nExclusive promotions and offers\nDirect Benefits:\n•\nMessages delivered\ninstantly\n, with a 98% open rate.\n•\nCustomers stayed informed, reducing queries and increasing satisfaction.\nLearn More\n1:1 Real-Time Support with Human Interaction\nAiSensy enabled live chat support on WhatsApp, allowing Cosco to:\n•\nDeliver\npersonalized and immediate responses\nto customer inquiries.\n•\nAddress questions about products, order tracking, and promotions in real time.\nResult:\nThis humanized and fast support boosted customer engagement by\n2x.\nLearn More\nBuilding Trust with the WhatsApp Blue Tick\nWith AiSensy’s help, Cosco secured the\nWhatsApp verified blue tick\n, allowing the company to:\n•\nShowcase\nauthenticity and trustworthiness\nto customers.\n•\nStrengthen its position as a credible brand, fostering long-term loyalty.\nLearn More\n24/7 Customer Support with Smart Chatbots\nCosco integrated AiSensy’s AI-driven chatbots, offering:\n• Round-the-clock assistance\n, available 24/7.\n•\nEasy-to-build conversation flows with a no-code drag-and-drop interface.\nImpact:\nChatbots ensured customers received timely support, even outside business hours, maintaining high-quality service.\nLearn More\n3\nX Better Reach\nBy sending Broadcasts on WhatsApp.\n2\nX Improved Engagement\nBy automating updates on WhatsApp and providing instant 1:1 support.\n98\n% Message Open Rate\n5x better than Emails & SMS.\n\"AiSensy has really helped us in terms of reaching our consumers. Earlier, the amount of users which we could reach via Broadcasting was somewhere around 30 to 35%. Now, the number has gone up to around 90% \"\nAakash Jain\nBusiness Executive at Cosco\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X ",
