      "url": "https://aisensy.com/case-studies/homelane",
      "title": "Homelane",
      "page_type": "blog",
      "summary": "HomeLane booked 300+ extra design consultations monthly by streamlining customer conversations on WhatsApp with AiSensy",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nDesign & Technology\nHeadquarters\nBengaluru, India\nCompany Size\n1,001 – 5,000 employees\nProducts\nModular kitchens, wardrobes & full-home interiors\nFragmented Appointment Journey\nSite visitors had to fill lengthy web forms and wait for call backs - many dropped off before scheduling design sessions. HomeLane's team had no way to reengage the lost lead.\nLower Conversion Efficiency\nTraditional channels (email/SMS) delivered just\n1.3 %\nlead-to-order conversion, limiting marketing ROI.\nAutomated WhatsApp Chat Assistant\nHow it works\n-\nInstant engagement, zero form fatigue\n.\n•\nVisitors click a “\nBook Free Design Session\n” button on the website.\n•\nThey land on WhatsApp & engage in conversation with a chatbot.\n•\nThe WhatsApp chatbot qualifies the lead, captures requirements and suggests available time slots.\n•\nConfirmed details are pushed to HomeLane’s CRM; human agents step in only when needed.\nLearn More\nStore Locator on WhatsApp\nHomelane increased their store visibility and footfall by adding a WhatsApp store locator.\nUsers can simply chat with the WhatsApp bot to find the nearest HomeLane store, get directions, and even schedule appointments - all within WhatsApp\n900\n+ New Qualified Leads / Month\nAutomated WhatsApp journeys pull in nearly a thousand extra prospects every month.\n2\nx Higher Lead-to-Order Conversion\nWhatsApp leads closed at\n2.8 %\n, versus\n1.3 %\nfrom other channels—doubling order wins.\n300\n+ Monthly Design Consults\nInstant booking flows secure\n300\nadditional pre-appointment slots each month, filling the sales calendar.\nWhatsApp based conversational campaigns have helped us enhance engagement with our customers. This has also resulted in better acquisition efficiency. Moreover, the insights from user interactions have been instrumental in shaping our new feature planning. In this journey, AISensy came handy as a powerful product for managing WhatsApp conversations & campaigns. The product interface significantly reduced our bot creation & deployment turnaround time.\nAbhishek Gupta\nVP Product\n@\nHomeLane\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X Your lead generations & 2-3X Conversions Instantly!\nRun Ads from AiSensy, smartly segregate your leads and build Chatbot Flows to automate everything!\nMultiple Human Live Chat\nHave multiple team members to drive Live Chat Support on the Same WhatsApp Business Number.\nFilter Chats according to tags, campaigns and attributes for Smart Agent Chat Routing.\nReal-Time Analytics\nTrack your campaign results in real-time.\nMonitor Read, Replied & Clicked rates for each campaign and retarget smartly for higher conversions!\nSmart Retargeting for 3X Sales\nSegregate your Audiences Smartly and Re-Broadcast for Higher Conversions!\nSports Equipment Brand\nHow Cosco, one of the",
