      "summary": "Explore how IndiaMART used WhatsApp to reduce their team's workload & achieve a massive 33% increase in buyer conversion rate - all via AiSensy.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nB2B Marketplace\nHeadquarters\nNoida, Uttar Pradesh\nProducts\nIndustrial machinery, consumer electronics, and apparel\nLearn More\n50 Lakh Enquiries Per Month\nIndiaMART receives\n50 lakh enquiries monthly\nfrom buyers across India. Their traditional process involved\ncalling each buyer\nto verify and approve their enquiries.\n2 Crore Calls Per month\nTo handle the immense enquiry volume, IndiaMART operated\n8 call centers\n, making\n2 crore calls monthly\nto connect with buyers.\nBuyer Irritation\nOn average, a buyer received\n4 calls per enquiry\n, leading to frustration, complaints, and blocked numbers.\nReplacing Outgoing Calls with WhatsApp Messages\nAiSensy enabled IndiaMART to replace time-consuming calls with\nWhatsApp messaging\n. This transition significantly reduced the team’s workload while maintaining high levels of buyer engagement.\nKey Features:\n•\nAutomated messages with chatbot integration.\n• Quick Replies\nand\nCTA Buttons\nfor seamless interactions.\nLearn More\nIntroduction of WhatsApp Forms\nWith AiSensy’s\nWhatsApp Forms\n, IndiaMART could:\n•\nCollect product preferences, quantities, and delivery details directly from buyers.\n•\nStreamline the enquiry and approval process without the need for repetitive calls.\nImpact:\n•\nFaster enquiry approval.\n•\nA smoother, more convenient buyer experience.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp Automation for Order Confirmations\nIndiaMART streamlined key operations using AiSensy, automating tasks such as:\n•\nOrder confirmations,\n•\nShipping updates,\n•\nDelivery notifications.\nThis automation saved time and maintained seamless, consistent communication with buyers.\nLearn More\n33\n% More Buyer Conversion\nWhatsApp 50L\nEnquiry approved 10L\n60\n% Less Complaints\nSince every buyer is getting just one WhatsApp message and not four calls on an everage - buyers stopped camplaining about being irritated\n3\nx More Customer Engagement\nOn WhatsApp and improved customer satisfaction\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X Your lead generations & 2-3X Conversions Instantly!\nRun Ads from AiSensy, smartly segregate your leads and build Chatbot Flows to automate everything!\nMultiple Human Live Chat\nHave multiple team members to drive Live Chat Support on the Same WhatsApp Business Number.\nFilter Chats according to tags, campaigns and attributes for Smart Agent Chat Routing.\nReal-Time Analytics\nTrack your campaign results in real-time.\nMonitor Read, Replied & Clicked rates for each campaign and retarget smartly for higher conversions!\nSmart Retargeting for 3X Sales\nSegregate your Audiences Smartly and Re-Broadcast for Higher Conversions!\nSports Equipment Brand\nHow Cosco, one of the most renowned Sporting equipment companies used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore conversions.\nExplore Case Study\nDonation Collection Platform\nDiscover ",
