      "summary": "Learn how NMIMS, a globally reputed University, generated 5x more leads & automated 83% of it's queries on WhatsApp with AiSensy.",
      "content": "Get Started for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nEducation\nHeadquarters\nMumbai, India\nStudents\n17000+ Students\nProgrammes\nOver 50 programmes offered\nLearn More\nHigh Application Drop-off Rate\n40% of the audience used to fill out the applications only till midway & left after filling only half the form.\nLow Attendance at Webinars & Events\nOnly 50-60% of the signed-up audience showed presence at webinars & events.\nLow Lead Generation & Qualification\nA good part of the audience left the website without sharing their email IDs or numbers. They hesitated to fill in their details.\nAutomate Drop-off Applications Reminders\nEarlier, NMIMS faced an application dropoff rate of 60%.\nTo recover this, they started automating Application Drop-off notification on WhatsApp to users who dropped off mid-way while filling out their applications.\nWith this drop-off notification alone, they were able to recover 45-60% of Drop-off applications.\nLearn More\nWebinars & Event Invitation / Reminders\nNMIMS wanted to increase engagement for Campus Events & Webinars.\nThey increased signups for their Events & Webinars by Broadcasting an Event/ Webinar invitation message on WhatsApp via AiSensy.\nBy doing this, NMIMS was able to drive\n3x more signups\nfor their Events & webinars.\nLearn More\nAutomate Attendance Notifications & Emergency Updates\nNMIMS understood that WhatsApp is the one-platform where their students were most active.\nThey started automating notifications for important updates, such as attendance, changes in class timings & other crucial notifications on WhatsApp.\nLearn More\nAutomate 83% repetitive queries with Chatbot\nTo make sure no queries are left unanswered, NMIMS automated 83% of their customer support with our Ai-driven Chatbots.\nThe chatbots are accessible 24/7, guaranteeing that users can receive support whenever they need it, including outside of standard business hours.\nBuilding conversation flows with AiSensy is very easy, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nReal-Time Customer Support on WhatsApp\nNMIMS students can now engage in 1:1 WhatsApp conversation for immediate support whenever they had queries. AiSensy's platform allowed multiple agents to manage chats from a single number, with easy conversation transfers, ensuring customers always reached the right person.\nThis efficient support led to a\n3x increase\nin customer engagement.\nLearn More\n5\nx Increase in Lead Generation\nWith AiSensy, NMIMS has successfully boosted lead generation by\n5x\n, amassing over\n45,000 qualified leads\n(and counting).\n45-\n60\n% Recovery in Application Drop-offs\n45-60% more applicants\ncompleted their sign-up process after receiving notification on WhatsApp to complete their application.\n3\nx Increase in Event & Webinar Signups\nNMIMS has also seen a\n3x\nrise in event and webinar sign-ups, thanks to timely WhatsApp notifications that remind participants of upcoming events, driving both attendance and engagement.\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes!",
