      "content": "Get Started for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nEdTech\nHeadquarters\nNew Delhi, India\nCompany Size\n1900+ Employees\nProducts\nOnline & Offline Coaching, Digital Courses & Study Materials\nLearn More\nDiminishing Conversions\nWith an open rate of just 20% and click-through rates between 2-5%, the results from email marketing weren't justifying the effort.\nDelayed Student Support and FAQs\nStudents found it challenging to get timely responses to their questions, causing frustration and hindering their learning experience.\nLow Webinar Attendance\nDespite registering for webinars, many users simply didn't show up.\nRunning Ads that Click to WhatsApp within AiSensy\nHow It Works:\n•\nLeads click on Instagram or Facebook ads.\n•\nLeads are redirected to a WhatsApp chat.\n•\nLeads initiate a conversation that triggers the chatbot.\n•\nLeads are automatically segmented into campaigns, engaged through broadcasts, chatbots, and catalogs, creating an efficient conversion flow.\nResults:\n3x more leads generated.\nLearn More\nBroadcast promotional offers to Unlimited Users\nUsing AiSensy, PhysicsWallah sent promotional offers to their entire contact base, including users who hadn’t saved the company’s number.\nImpact:\n5x more course sales and significant engagement.\nLearn More\nBuild Personalized Customer Relationships with Customers\nUsing AiSensy's intuitive 1:1 live chat, customers were able to easily inquire about courses and receive instant updates.\nAiSensy enabled multiple agents to manage chats from a single number, with easy transfer of conversations to ensure customers always reached the right person.\nBenefit:\nCloser relationships, greater trust, and an enhanced experience.\nLearn more\nAutomated WhatsApp Reminders\nAutomated reminders sent via WhatsApp kept students engaged and ensured higher attendance at webinars.\nResult:\nWebinar attendance increased by 4x, boosting retention and the impact of sessions.\nLearn More\nAutomate Common Queries with WhatsApp Chatbot\nPhysicsWallah implemented a WhatsApp chatbot to answer frequently asked questions quickly and effectively.\nDirect Benefit:\nFreed up valuable time for the team to focus on critical demands, resulting in improved student support.\nLearn More\n3\nx Leads Generated\nby running Ads that Click to WhatsApp\n4\nx Webinar attendance\nby sending reminders on WhatsApp\n5\nx Course sales\nwith WhatsApp Broadcasting\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X Your lead generations & 2-3X Conversions Instantly!\nRun Ads from AiSensy, smartly segregate your leads and build Chatbot Flows to automate everything!\nMultiple Human Live Chat\nHave multiple team members to drive Live Chat Support on the Same WhatsApp Business Number.\nFilter Chats according to tags, campaigns and attributes for Smart Agent Chat Routing.\nReal-Time Analytics\nTrack your campa",
