      "content": "Get Started for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nEcommerce\nHeadquarters\nPark City, Utah\nCompany Size\n300-500 Employees\nProducts\nEarphones, headphones, Wireless Earbuds\nLearn More\nIncreasing Abandoned Carts\nUsers visiting the website added products to their cart but did not complete the purchase.\nReduced ROI\nSending\npersonalized emails & SMS\ndid not have an efficient enough ROI for Skullcandy.\nSiloed Customer Support\nSkullcandy had no direct source to communicate with customers in real-time.\n1:1 Live Chat\nwas not much effective via Website Chat!\n25-40% Abandoned Carts Recovered\nTo solve the dilemma of Abandoned Carts, AiSensy set up WhatsApp automation,\nconnecting Skullcandy's Ecommerce store with AiSensy\n.\nThis integration triggered an\nAbandoned Cart recovery notification\n15-20 minutes after a user added a product to their cart & didn't complete the transaction.\nThis strategy helped Skullcandy recover\n25-40% of Abandoned Carts\n.\nBroadcast Promotional Offers to Unlimited Users in One Go\nUsing AiSensy's intuitive platform, Skullcandy seamlessly broadcasted marketing and promotional offers to their entire customer base — reaching users even if they hadn’t added Skullcandy to their contacts.\nBy adhering to WhatsApp’s best practices, Skullcandy successfully delivered WhatsApp messages to an unlimited number of users, all without the risk of being blocked.\nAutomate Order & Delivery Updates on WhatsApp\nWith AiSensy, Skullcandy has automated the sending of:\n• Order confirmations\ndirectly via WhatsApp, eliminating the need for emails or SMS.\n• Delivery updates\nin real time, ensuring that customers have quick and convenient access to information.\n150\nx ROI\nDriven with WhatsApp Marketing\n25-\n40\n%\nIncrease in Abandoned Cart Recovery\n3\nX\nUser Engagement seen on messages sent\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X Your lead generations & 2-3X conversions instantly!\nRun Ads from AiSensy, smartly segregate your leads and build Chatbot Flows to automate everything!\nMultiple Human Live Chat\nHave multiple team members to drive Live Chat Support on the Same WhatsApp Business Number.\nFilter Chats according to tags, campaigns and attributes for Smart Agent Chat Routing.\nReal-Time Analytics\nTrack your campaign results in real-time.\nMonitor Read, Replied & Clicked rates for each campaign and retarget smartly for higher conversions!\nSmart Retargeting for 3X Sales\nSegregate your Audiences Smartly and Re-Broadcast for Higher Conversions!\nSports Equipment Brand\nHow Cosco, one of the most renowned Sporting equipment companies used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore conversions.\nExplore Case Study\nDonation Collection Platform\nDiscover how Give, India's most trusted donations collection platform used WhatsApp to achieve a\n90% Payment success rate\n&\n15X ROI\n.\nExplore Case Study\nEdtech",
