      "summary": "Learn how Thyrocare used WhatsApp automation to increase patient engagement, boost diagnostic bookings, and streamline communication.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIndustry\nHealthcare & Diagnostics\nPlatform\nBookMyTest – Digital diagnostics booking platform\nServices\nDiagnostic test discovery, booking, and patient engagement\nWebsite\nFragmented Communication Systems\nBefore implementing AiSensy, Thyrocare relied on multiple communication channels such as SMS, RCS, and standalone WhatsApp tools. This fragmented setup made it difficult to manage patient conversations centrally and maintain consistent service quality.\nOperational Inefficiencies in Handling Patient Queries\nAs BookMyTest began receiving thousands of patient interactions daily, managing queries manually became increasingly inefficient. Teams struggled to respond quickly while handling high volumes of booking inquiries and support requests.\nLimited Visibility and Slow Response Times\nWithout a unified platform, Thyrocare had limited visibility into conversations and response performance. This led to slower response times, impacting patient experience and reducing potential diagnostic booking conversions.\nUnified Patient Communication\nThyrocare\npartnered with AiSensy to implement a\nscalable WhatsApp Business API infrastructure\nfor BookMyTest.\nUsing AiSensy’s\nmulti-agent live chat\n, multiple support agents could handle patient conversations simultaneously from one number, ensuring faster response times.\nClick-to-WhatsApp Lead Capture\nPatients arriving from ads or the website could instantly start a WhatsApp conversation, making test inquiries and bookings faster and more convenient.\nBroadcast Campaigns for Patient Engagement\nThe team ran broadcast campaigns for:\nDiagnostic packages\nSeasonal health checkups\nPromotional offers\nTest reminders\nThis enabled direct engagement with opted-in patients at scale.\nRich Interactive Messages\nCarousel messages and button-based interactions allowed patients to explore packages and book tests directly from WhatsApp.\nLearn More\n24/7 Customer Support with Smart Chatbots\nThyrocare integrated AiSensy’s AI-driven chatbots, offering:\n• Round-the-clock assistance\n, available 24/7.\n•\nEasy-to-build conversation flows with a no-code drag-and-drop interface.\nImpact:\nChatbots ensured customers received timely support, even outside business hours, maintaining high-quality service.\n40\n% Increase in Booking Conversions\nAutomated conversations and instant responses significantly increased patient booking completion rates.\n5\nx Increase in Engagement\nDaily WhatsApp interactions grew from\n30–40 users to over 200–300 active conversations\n, dramatically improving patient reach.\n2\nx Operational Efficiency\nBy automating conversations and centralizing communication, Thyrocare was able to\nhandle significantly higher patient volumes without increasing team size\n.\nCollect Payments on WhatsApp\nYes! Collect Payments now on WhatsApp Seamlessly with WhatsApp Pay and other modes of Payments (Razorpay, Payu etc) and grow your revenue.\nAds that Click to WhatsApp\nRun Ads on Facebook & Instagram that land on WhatsApp. 5X Your lea",
