      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features",
      "title": "AiSensy Platform Features & Product Overview (WhatsApp Business API)",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Check out High-revenue features of AiSensy that make it the Smartest WhatsApp Marketing Platform for your business.",
      "content": "Smooth Chatbot to Human Transfer\nMonitor Chatbot Conversations and Take over the Conversation smoothly. Get Notified when for Bot to Human Transfers\nSmart Audience Segmentation\nNo Need to Upload Excel Each time you wish to broadcast! Segregate Audiences using Filters and Broadcast Accordingly.\nDrag & Drop Chatbots\nBuild dynamic drag & drop WhatsApp Chatbots easily in just 10 minutes\nBook a Demo Now\nExtensive User Profile & CRM\nBe available for your customers on their favourite WhatsApp channel 24/7 using NLP based Chatbot and Live Chat. 🤖\nFilter Chats according to tags, campaigns and attributes for Smart Agent Chat Routing.\nTrack Clicks on WhatsApp Broadcasts\nTrack the number of users who are clicking your WhatsApp Broadcast & drive 3x more conversions by Retargeting!\nBuild no-code Chatbot in minutes\nBuild your Own Chatbot Flows your Way! Easy-to-use Chatbot & Catalog Flow builder to build your conversational journeys\nSend Automated CTA Based Notifications\nWhatsapp Smart Notifications include Quick Links & Quick Reply Call-to-Action Buttons with 45-60% Click Rates.\nDrive 5x Leads with Click to WhatsApp Ads\nCreate Facebook/ Instagram Ads directly via AiSensy and reduce cost per lead by 60%.\nIntegrations that Drive Growth\nAutomate Smart Notifications using AiSensy via Zapier, Shopify, WooCommerce, Hubspot, Salesforce, Payment Portals, Custom CRM & more.\nSmart Retargeting for 3X Sales\nSegregate your Audiences Smartly and Re-Broadcast for Higher Conversions!\nImport & Broadcast Instantly\nSimply Import all your Contacts and Broadcast approved messages Instantly.\nSee real-time analytics on the AiSensy Platform for delivered, read rates and more\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Support on the same Whatsapp number.\nLearn More\nChatbot Flow\nBuilder\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nRetarget\nUsers on WhatsApp\nAiSensy’s WhatsApp Retarget feature allows you to segregate your audience and Re-Broadcast for higher conversions.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nScheduler\nSchedule Broadcasts up to 2 months ahead of time across varying timezones.\nLearn More\nImport, Broadcast &\nTrack\nTrack users clicking on your message's CTA buttons with this Pro Feature.\nLearn More\nAds that\nClick\nto WhatsApp\nDrive 5x More Leads with Ads that Click to WhatsApp.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nWebviews\nLoad web pages directly within WhatsApp. No more losing customers to external browsers.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nForms\nCreate and send forms with this native integration. Capture leads, book appointments, collect feedback, and more.\nLearn More\nExplore Plans And Pricing\nFREE WhatsApp Business API\nGet Whatsapp Business API Approval in 10 Minutes (FREE with any plan).\nBroadcast Unlimited Campaigns\nBroadcast Messages to Unlimited users every day.\nConnect No Code A.I. Chatbots\nConnect No-Code Chatbots from Google Dialogflow in a Single Click.\nMulti-Agent Live Chat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat ",
