      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features/ai-ad-creative-generator",
      "title": "AI Ad Creative Generator",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Generate brand-ready ad creatives for your WhatsApp campaigns in seconds. Just add a prompt, upload your logo, and watch AI work its magic.",
      "content": "Start FREE – ₹500 Credits Included\nBook a Demo\nAdd a short prompt\nDescribe what you want to create\nUpload Brand Assets\nUpload your logo and product image\nGenerate & Launch\nGet stunning Ad creatives personalized for your brand\nOpen AiSensy App\nOpen the AiSensy App. New users can create a free account without providing credit card information.\nThe free account includes permanent access to the CTWA Manager plus 500 AI credits and 3 bonus generations to test the Ad Generator.\nFor full platform capabilities, a 14-day trial is available.\nOpen AiSensy App\nGo to\nAI Ad Creative Generator\nFrom the left sidebar, go to \"\nAds Manager\n\" and Click on \"\n+Create Ad\n\".\nIf it's your first time, you will need to connect your Facebook account to the WhatsApp API number. Follow the prompts in the Setup tab to complete this one-time configuration.\nWrite your Prompt\nDescribe what you want to create. Detailed prompts produce better results.\nExample:\n“Generate a promotional message for a D2C brand - TeeHub Studios promotion our exclusive Avengers T-shirt collection, with an early bird discount of 20%\".\nInsert Image Assets\nUpload your logo and product image. The AI uses this to ensure generated ads align with your visual identity.\nSupported formats include PNG and JPG.\nGenerate & Launch Your Ad\nIn a few seconds, boom, you get ready-to-use Ad creatives personalized for your brand.\nAdjust your prompt if you like or move on to the final step of your setup process, which includes refining your target audience, budget, and schedule.\nEach generation uses 50 AI credits and produces three images. New accounts receive 3 free generations + 500 AI credits.\nTry it for FREE\nAI Ads Creative Generator\nInstantly generate stunning visuals and ad creatives. Transform your ideas into high-quality images with a simple text prompt.\nLearn More\nAI Video Generator\nCreate engaging, professional-quality videos in minutes. Turn your text into captivating video content for your campaigns.\nComing Soon\nAI Template Message Generator\nCraft high-converting, pre-approved WhatsApp templates in seconds. Reduce rejection rates and boost your campaign's engagement.\nLearn More\nAI Chatbot Flows Generator\nDesign and build intelligent chatbot conversations with ease. Automate your customer interactions with our no-code flow builder.\nLearn More\nExcellent\n4.4\nour of\n5\nbased on\n660 reviews\nUNESCO – World Heritage Bot\nDeployed on WhatsApp, this AI Agent delivers educational content on Indian heritage sites in\n19+ languages\n. Combining\nvoice and text\n, it makes cultural knowledge accessible to students, tourists, and history enthusiasts worldwide—proving AI can scale learning globally.\nRead More\nAnkur Warikoo – Creator & Educator\nEntrepreneur Ankur Warikoo uses AiSensy’s AI Chatbot to\nautomate WhatsApp conversations\nwith his community. The AI Agent provides\ninstant, personalized responses\n, allowing him to nurture and grow his audience at scale—without losing the human touch.\nRead More\nSunfeast Dark Fantasy\nSunfeast Da",
