      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Create engaging video ads in seconds with AI. Turn prompts, product images, or logos into scroll-stopping video ads optimized for social media platforms.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nAdd a short prompt\nUpload your logo or product image\nGet stunning videos ads personalized for your brand\nOpen AiSensy App\nOpen you AiSensy App, then go to '\nAds Manager\n' and click on '\n+Create Ad\n'.\nIf you don't have an AiSensy account, you can create one for free.\nOpen AiSensy App\nClick on\nAI Video Ad Generator\nTool\nAdd a Short Prompt\n→ e.g., “Generate a high-energy video showcasing stylish clothing items with models wearing them in various trendy settings.”\nUpload Logo or Product Image\n→ Keep your branding consistent.\nAdjust Settings\n→ Choose screen size, audience, character, and CTA\nClick Generate\n→ Instantly get multiple video ad variations.\nGenerate & Launch Your Video Ad\nInstantly, our AI will generate video ads tailored to your inputs. Refine it if needed, and launch it to start engaging your customers and driving conversions.\nAI Ads Creative Generator\nInstantly generate stunning visuals and ad creatives. Transform your ideas into high-quality images with a simple text prompt.\nLearn More\nAI Video Generator\nCreate engaging, professional-quality videos in minutes. Turn your text into captivating video content for your campaigns.\nLearn More\nVoice Calling AI\nAutomate and enhance your customer calls. Provide instant, AI-powered responses and support to your customers 24/7.\nLearn More\nAI Template Message Generator\nCraft high-converting, pre-approved WhatsApp templates in seconds. Reduce rejection rates and boost your campaign's engagement.\nLearn More\nAI Chatbot Flows Generator\nDesign and build intelligent chatbot conversations with ease. Automate your customer interactions with our no-code flow builder.\nLearn More\nExcellent\n4.4\nour of\n5\nbased on\n660 reviews\nUNESCO – World Heritage Bot\nDeployed on WhatsApp, this AI Agent delivers educational content on Indian heritage sites in\n19+ languages\n. Combining\nvoice and text\n, it makes cultural knowledge accessible to students, tourists, and history enthusiasts worldwide—proving AI can scale learning globally.\nRead More\nAnkur Warikoo – Creator & Educator\nEntrepreneur Ankur Warikoo uses AiSensy’s AI Chatbot to\nautomate WhatsApp conversations\nwith his community. The AI Agent provides\ninstant, personalized responses\n, allowing him to nurture and grow his audience at scale—without losing the human touch.\nRead More\nSunfeast Dark Fantasy\nSunfeast Dark Fantasy uses an AI WhatsApp chatbot to power\nfun, personalized fan engagement\n. Consumers chat with the bot, upload selfies, and receive Fantasy Avatars—while Click-to-WhatsApp Ads seamlessly drive participation, boosting campaign reach and brand connection.\nRead More\nTry AiSensy for FREE\nBook a Demo\nWhat is the AI Video Ad Generator?\nIt’s a tool that creates short, branded video ads from prompts, logos, or product images—optimized for Facebook and Instagram.\nHow does it connect with WhatsApp marketing?\nVideos are built for Click-to-WhatsApp ads, turning social media engagement into direct WhatsApp conversations.\nDo I need video editin",
