      "content": "Request Callback\nMulti-Language Support\nSupports text, voice, image & video\nIntegrates with payments, CRMs, and backend systems\nAI WhatsApp Chatbot\nHuman Agent\nTraditional Chatbot\nAI WhatsApp Chatbot\nHuman Agent\nTraditional Chatbot\nIntelligence\nLearns from interactions, understands context & intent using NLP\nHighest – full understanding, reasoning, empathy\nRule-based, keyword-triggered responses\nSpeed\nNear-instant replies (<1 sec)\nMinutes to hours (depends on availability)\nFast, but limited to predefined flows\nScalability\nHandles thousands of concurrent chats\n1–2 chats at a time\nScales well, but within rigid paths\nAvailability\n24/7, 365 days a year\nBusiness hours only (shift-based)\n24/7, but only for scripted queries\nEmotional Intelligence\nDetects sentiment, responds empathetically (basic)\nDeep empathy, active listening, emotional support\nNone – no understanding of tone or mood\nBest Use Case\nRoutine queries, multilingual support, order tracking, payments\nComplex issues, complaints, sales, emotional support\nSimple FAQs, menu-based navigation, static info delivery\nText to Text\nProvides AI-generated text responses to written queries\nText to Voice\nConverts text into human-like voice messages\nVoice to Text\nTranscribes voice notes and replies with text\nVoice to Voice\nFully voice-based conversations\nImage Response\nShares AI-generated images based on user queries\nVideo Response\nResponds with AI-generated video content for enhanced experience\nCustomer support for Any Business\nEnhance customer satisfaction with 24/7 personalized product recommendations,  frequently asked questions about orders, and secure payments.\nSmart Product Recommendations for E-commerce\nSend personalized suggestions based on user behavior, preferences and history of puchases. .\nSugere produtos personalizados com base no comportamento, preferências e histórico do usuário.\nHelp users choose the most suitable plan or product by understanding their needs and preferences. Improve conversion rates by offering tailored recommendations that guide prospects toward the right solution.\nEffortless appointment for Real Estate Agents\nStreamline client bookings by collecting details and automatically syncing appointments with your calendar. Reduce scheduling conflicts and no-shows while providing a seamless booking experience.\nAccount management for Banks\nQuickly handle balance inquiries, transaction alerts, and fund transfers. Enhance banking efficiency with instant communication and personalized customer service that operates 24/7.\nFeedback collection for Education\nGather valuable insights on courses, instructors, and facilities through an interactive Q&A approach. Increase response rates and enhance engagement with real-time, personalized interactions.\nHuman-like Customer Support\nDelight customers with fast, empathetic, and context-aware conversations that feel like chatting with a real agent.\nSmart Product Recommendations\nBoost sales with spot-on recommendations based on user behavior, history ",
