    {
      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features/aisensy-meta-ads-manager",
      "title": "Aisensy Meta Ads Manager",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "All-in-one Meta Ads platform built for businesses. Run Click-to-WhatsApp Ads, Website Ads, and Lead Form Ads—all from one intuitive dashboard powered by the official WhatsApp Business API.",
      "content": "Start Free |\nGet ₹500 Ad Credits\nBook a Demo\nClick-to-WhatsApp Ads\nDrive conversations. CTA button opens a WhatsApp chat with your business. Perfect for engagement, lead nurturing, and customer support.\nLearn More\nWebsite Ads\nDrive traffic. CTA button opens external websites, landing pages, or product pages. Ideal for traffic generation and sales.\nLearn More\nLead Form Ads\nCapture leads. CTA button opens a form within Meta platforms. Zero friction, highest conversion rates. Best for B2B lead generation.\nLearn More\nUnified Campaign Management\nManage your entire marketing funnel from one platform. Use AiSensy Ads Manager to run Meta Ads, then use AiSensy's automation to nurture those visitors via WhatsApp.\nAdvanced Audience Targeting\nReach people by location, demographics, interests, behaviors, and lookalike audiences. Alternatively, upload your customer list or create website visitor audiences.\nManage & Buy More Ad Credits\nAll AiSensy users start with\n₹500 in Meta Ads credits\n. Once you've used your credits, you can easily purchase more directly within the AiSensy platform without leaving the dashboard.\nReal-time analytics and performance tracking\nTrack key performance indicators, such as Impressions, Reach, Clicks, CTR, CPC, and Total Spend.\nOpen AiSensy App\nOpen the AiSensy App. New users can create a free account without providing credit card information.\nThe free account includes permanent access to the Ads Manager + ₹ 500 Meta Ads credits + ₹50 Free WhatsApp Conversation Credits.\nOpen AiSensy App\nGo to Ads Manager & connect your Facebook Business Manager\nGo to \"Ads Manager\" in the left sidebar and connect your Facebook Business Manager. Select the Facebook page through which you want to run Website Ads.\nLearn More\nSelect Ad Type\nClick \"+ Create Ad\" and Choose Click-to-WhatsApp, Website, or Lead Form Ad based on your campaign objective (Traffic, Engagement, Sales, Leads).\nTarget Your Audience\nSelect geo-location, age, gender, interests, and behaviors. Choose platforms (Instagram & Facebook) and placements (Feed, Stories, Explore, Reels, Marketplace).\nSet Budget & Duration\nDefine your daily budget and campaign duration. Track ad credits in real-time.\nAdd Visuals & Copy\nFill in ad details and upload creative.\nOptionally, use\nAI Ad Creative Generator\nto create professional visuals in seconds.\nAI Ad Creative Generator\nSubmit & Monitor Performance\nClick \"Publish\" to submit your ad for approval. Facebook typically approves ads within 15-20 minutes. Monitor performance in the Ads Manager dashboard.\nLaunch & Monitor Campaign\nGo to Ads Manager to view your Ad status. If your Ad gets rejected, you can view the rejection reason in your Facebook Ads account. If approved, you're ready to launch.\nThat's it!\nIt's time to start creating Ads on Facebook/ Instagram via AiSensy & drive leads to your WhatsApp Business account.\nExcellent\n4.4\nour of\n5\nbased on\n660 reviews\nAdd a short prompt\nDescribe what you want to create\nUpload Brand Assets\nUpload your logo and pr",
