      "title": "Click Tracking",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "See exactly who clicks your WhatsApp links. AiSensy's click tracking feature helps you analyse user behaviour and optimise marketing with real-time insights.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nReal-Time Click Analytics\nInstantly monitor who clicks and how many times they click\nEffortless One-Click Retargeting\nSend Retargeting Campaigns to clicked users in one tap\n3x Conversions. 2x Less Cost\nRetarget only high-intent users, save money, drive 3x more conversions.Get Started TodayInsert a page componentAsk AIEdit component\nUnlock Click Tracking\nSignup on AiSensy\nCreate your AiSensy account.\nApply for FREE WhatsApp Business API.\nCreate Account\nCreate WhatsApp Template Messages\nCreate & Submit WhatsApp Template messages\nLearn More\nSend WhatsApp Broadcast\nSend a WhatsApp Broadcast message with Clickable CTA Button.\nNote:\nYou can only track clicks on URL CTA buttons through the Click Tracking feature.\nClicks on\nCall Now\nbutton containing number can't be tracked.\nLearn More\nVisit Campaigns Page\nClick \"Go to Campaign\" and tap on \"Clicked\" Audience\nGo to \"Clicked\" Tab\nHere you can view the audience that clicked on the URL-based CTA Button as well as how many times a user clicked it.\nRetarget Clicked Users\nLastly, select clicked users and send retargeting campaign to these high-intent users!!\nDoing this, you're on your way to drive 3 times more conversions from your WhatsApp Broadcast while saving money.\nLearn More\nUnlock Flow Builder\nPriya Ostwal\nMarketing Manager, PhysicsWallah\nAiSensy team has shown exceptional professionalism, reliability and a true commitment to customer satisfaction.\nAkash Jain\nBusiness Executive, Cosco\nAiSensy helped us increase our customer engagement. Our customer engagement increased from\n35% to 90%\nwith AiSensy's Smart Retargeting feature.\nAchina Mayya\nFounder & CEO, AevyTV\nAiSensy has been pivotal for us. The personalised interactions and instant responses greatly improved our engagement rates, and more importantly our sales!\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Support on the same Whatsapp number.\nLearn More\nChatbot Flow\nBuilder\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nRetarget\nUsers on WhatsApp\nAiSensy’s WhatsApp Retarget feature allows you to segregate your audience and Re-Broadcast for higher conversions.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nScheduler\nSchedule Broadcasts up to 2 months ahead of time across varying timezones.\nLearn More\nImport, Broadcast &\nTrack\nTrack users clicking on your message's CTA buttons with this Pro Feature.\nLearn More\nAds that\nClick\nto WhatsApp\nDrive 5x More Leads with Ads that Click to WhatsApp.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nWebviews\nLoad web pages directly within WhatsApp. No more losing customers to external browsers.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nForms\nCreate and send forms with this native integration. Capture leads, book appointments, collect feedback, and more.\nLearn More\nExcellent\n4.4\nour of\n5\nbased on\n660 reviews",
