      "content": "Start Free |\nGet ₹500 Ad Credits\nBook a Demo\nBook a demo\nUnified Campaign Management\nManage your entire marketing funnel from one platform. Run Website Ads to drive traffic, then use AiSensy's automation to nurture those visitors via WhatsApp.\nAdvanced Audience Targeting\nReach people by location, demographics, interests, behaviors, and lookalike audiences. Alternatively, upload your customer list or create website visitor audiences.\nManage & Buy More Ad Credits\nAll AiSensy users start with\n₹500 in Meta Ads credits\n. Once you've used your credits, you can easily purchase more directly within the AiSensy platform without leaving the dashboard.\nReal-time analytics and performance tracking\nTrack key performance indicators, such as Impressions, Reach, Clicks, CTR, CPC, and Total Spend.\nUse Website Ads for:\nDriving traffic to your website or blog\nPromoting product launches or new features\nCapturing email sign-ups via landing pages\nIncreasing website conversions\nBuilding brand awareness and reach\nConsider other ads if you want to:\nInitiate direct conversations (Click-to-WhatsApp)\nCapture lead data without leaving Meta platforms (Lead Form Ads)\nBuild relationships through WhatsApp engagement\nOpen AiSensy App\nOpen the AiSensy App. New users can create a free account without providing credit card information.\nThe free account includes permanent access to the Ads Manager + ₹ 500 Meta Ads credits + ₹50 Free WhatsApp Conversation Credits.\nOpen AiSensy App\nGo to Ads Manager & connect your Facebook Business Manager\nGo to \"Ads Manager\" in the left sidebar and connect your Facebook Business Manager. Select the Facebook page through which you want to run Website Ads.\nLearn More\nChoose Website Ad Type\nClick \"+ Create Ad\" and select \"Website Ad\" from the ad type options. This tells AiSensy to direct users to your website.\nAdd your Meta Pixel to enable accurate tracking and better optimization.\nTarget Your Audience\nSelect geo-location, gender, age group, interests, and behaviors. Choose platforms (Instagram and/or Facebook) and placements (Feed, Stories, Explore, Reels, Marketplace).\nSet Budget & Duration\nChoose your daily budget and select the time period for your ad campaign. Track remaining ad credits in real-time.\nAdd your Visuals & Copy\nUpload your visuals and fill in Ad Name, Primary Text, Headline, and add destination URL (where you want users to be directed, e.g., Landing Page)\nOptionally, use\nAI Ad Creative Generator\nto create professional visuals in seconds.\nAI Ad Creative Generator\nSubmit for Approval & Launch\nClick \"Publish\" to submit your ad for approval. Facebook typically approves ads within 15-20 minutes. Monitor performance in the Ads Manager dashboard.\nLaunch & Monitor Campaign\nGo to\nAds Manager\nto view your Ad status. If your Ad gets rejected, you can view the rejection reason in your Facebook Ads account. If approved, you're ready to launch.\nThat's it!\nIt's time to start creating Ads on Facebook/ Instagram via AiSensy & drive leads to your WhatsAp",
