      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features/voice-calling-ai",
      "title": "Voice Calling AI",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Talk to Customers with AI-Powered Voice Agents. Automate outbound and inbound calls on WhatsApp or phone with natural, human-like AI voices—available 24/7.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nAutomate Calls\nRun outbound reminders, surveys, or promotions automatically.\nOffer 24/7 Support\nNever miss customer queries, even outside working hours.\nScale Conversations\nHandle thousands of calls simultaneously without extra staff.\nSpeak Their Language\nMultilingual support for diverse audiences.\nPayment Collections\nFriendly, AI-driven reminders to complete payments.\nCustomer Support\nAnswer FAQs instantly via natural voice interactions.\nSurveys & Feedback\nCollect responses quickly through conversational voice bots.\nWhatsApp + Voice Combo\nStart with a Click-to-WhatsApp ad, continue with AI voice follow-up.\nAppointment Reminders\nReduce no-shows with automated voice calls.\nAI Ads Creative Generator\nInstantly generate stunning visuals and ad creatives. Transform your ideas into high-quality images with a simple text prompt.\nLearn More\nAI Video Generator\nCreate engaging, professional-quality videos in minutes. Turn your text into captivating video content for your campaigns.\nLearn More\nAI Template Message Generator\nCraft high-converting, pre-approved WhatsApp templates in seconds. Reduce rejection rates and boost your campaign's engagement.\nLearn More\nAI Chatbot Flows Generator\nDesign and build intelligent chatbot conversations with ease. Automate your customer interactions with our no-code flow builder.\nLearn More\nExcellent\n4.4\nour of\n5\nbased on\n660 reviews\nUNESCO – World Heritage Bot\nDeployed on WhatsApp, this AI Agent delivers educational content on Indian heritage sites in\n19+ languages\n. Combining\nvoice and text\n, it makes cultural knowledge accessible to students, tourists, and history enthusiasts worldwide—proving AI can scale learning globally.\nRead More\nAnkur Warikoo – Creator & Educator\nEntrepreneur Ankur Warikoo uses AiSensy’s AI Chatbot to\nautomate WhatsApp conversations\nwith his community. The AI Agent provides\ninstant, personalized responses\n, allowing him to nurture and grow his audience at scale—without losing the human touch.\nRead More\nSunfeast Dark Fantasy\nSunfeast Dark Fantasy uses an AI WhatsApp chatbot to power\nfun, personalized fan engagement\n. Consumers chat with the bot, upload selfies, and receive Fantasy Avatars—while Click-to-WhatsApp Ads seamlessly drive participation, boosting campaign reach and brand connection.\nRead More\nTry AiSensy for FREE\nBook a Demo\nWhat is Voice Calling AI?\nIt’s an AI-powered system that automates outbound and inbound customer calls using natural, human-like voices in multiple languages.\nHow does it integrate with WhatsApp?\nVoice AI can deliver voice notes and respond to queries on WhatsApp, or follow up Click-to-WhatsApp ads with calls.\nCan customers speak back to the AI?\nYes. The AI Voice Agent understands responses and continues the conversation naturally, or hands over to a human agent if needed.\nWhat kind of calls can I run?\nEverything from appointment reminders and payment follow-ups to surveys, onboarding, and customer support queries.\nIs it available 24/7?\nYes. V",
