      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Deploy smart WhatsApp AI agents to capture leads, recommend products, complete tasks, manage orders, and achieve goals without any coding.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nStart for FREE\nBook a Demo\nStart for FREE\nBook a Demo\n24/7 replies\nAlways available\nContext-base response\nUnderstands contexts and replies according to user queries\nHuman handoff\nEscalates to humans when needed\nAI Agent vs\nBasic Keyword Chatbot\nSee exactly how AiSensy AI Agent goes beyond basic chatbots to deliver real business results.\nFeature\nBasic Keyword Chatbot\nAiSensy AI Agent\nRecommended\nQuery Understanding\n✕\nWorks only on exact keyword matches\n✓\nUnderstands natural customer intent\nCustomer Experience\n✕\nRobotic and rigid conversations\n✓\nHuman-like conversational experience\nContext Awareness\n✕\nCannot understand conversation context\n✓\nUnderstands context across conversations\nResponse Type\n✕\nSends predefined static replies\n✓\nGenerates dynamic AI-powered responses\nReal-Time Data Access\n✕\nCannot fetch live data\n✓\nFetches live data from APIs, CRMs, Shopify, etc.\nWorkflow Actions\n✕\nLimited to predefined chatbot flows\n✓\nCan trigger APIs and automate actions\nAI Routing\n✕\nCannot intelligently route conversations\n✓\nRoutes customers to the right AI agent based on intent and context\nLead Qualification\n✕\nRequires manual rule-based flows\n✓\nQualifies leads intelligently using AI\nSales Assistance\n✕\nLimited static recommendations\n✓\nRecommends products and guides customers toward purchases\nAppointment Booking\n✕\nRequires separate manual flows\n✓\nBooks and confirms appointments automatically\nSetup Time\n✕\nHours of manual flow building\n✓\nLaunch AI agents in minutes\nMulti-Language Support\n✕\nLimited keyword dependency\n✓\nUnderstands multiple languages naturally\nSign up to AiSensy\nHead over to\naisensy.com\nand create a free AiSensy account.\nSign Up\nGo to Flows & Click Create Flow\nNavigate to the Flows section in your AiSensy dashboard. Click on Create Flow to start building your AI Agent from scratch or use a template.\nUpload Your Help Docs or Add Website Link\nOpen the Knowledge Base tab. Add your website URL, upload PDFs, or create articles directly. AiSensy will auto-index your content for the AI to use.\nSet Instructions in AI Orchestrator\nTell your AI how to behave — define your business context, tone, workflow rules, and restrictions. The AI will follow these instructions in every conversation.\nYour AI Agent is Ready to Go\nThat's it! Your WhatsApp AI Agent is now live and ready to answer customer queries 24/7. Test it, refine it, and watch it handle conversations like a pro.\nCustomer support for Any Business\nEnhance customer satisfaction with 24/7 personalized product recommendations,  frequently asked questions about orders, and secure payments.\nSmart Product Recommendations for E-commerce\nSend personalized suggestions based on user behavior, preferences and history of puchases. .\nSugere produtos personalizados com base no comportamento, preferências e histórico do usuário.\nHelp users choose the most suitable plan or product by understanding their needs and preferences. Improve conversion rates by offering tailored recommendations that ",
