      "summary": "Automate repetitive tasks like collecting user feedback, abandoned cart reminders & more with WhatsApp automation powered by AiSensy.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\n1. The Trigger (Event)\nAn action taken by a user or an event in your system (e.g., a customer adds an item to their cart but leaves the website, or someone sends \"Hi\" to your WhatsApp number).\n2. The Logic (Flow)\nThe predefined rule or chatbot flow created in AiSensy’s no-code builder. It dictates what should happen next based on the trigger (e.g., \"Wait 15 minutes, then send a discount code\").\n3.The Action (Response)\nThe automated WhatsApp message instantly delivered to the user's phone with an unmatched 98% open rate.\nTurn Leads into Customers Effortlessly\nLet your chatbot do the heavy lifting by qualifying leads easily, driving conversions without human intervention.\nA Chatbot Builder for Non-techies\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\n24x7 Support & Sales Automation on WhatsApp\nAutomate Support & Sales processes with dynamic Chatbots answering your customer's common queries, helping them arrive at the sales decision 3x faster!\nSeamless Integration with Business Tools\nConnect WhatsApp with your CRM, eCommerce platforms, and other tools to automate workflows and ensure consistency across channels.\n98\n%\nOpen Rates\n45-\n60\n%\nClick Rates\n3\nBn+\nActive Users\n7\n%\nEngagement Rate\nLearn More\neCommerce\nAutomate marketing campaigns, abandoned cart reminders, and order updates to boost sales and customer retention.\nHealthcare\nStreamline appointment scheduling, send reminders, and provide instant responses to patient inquiries.\nEducation\nEngage students with automated course reminders, enrollment updates, and 24/7 support.\nHospitality\nImprove guest services with automated booking confirmations, check-in/out reminders, and customer support.\nFinance & Fintech\nEnhance client communication with automated payment reminders, transaction alerts, and account updates.\nAutomotive\nSchedule test drives, send service reminders, and provide instant support. Explore how WhatsApp can transform your automotive business's CX.\nReal Estate\nAutomate property inquiries, instantly share listings with images/videos, schedule site visits, send reminders, and follow up with potential buyers.\nFood & Beverage\nSend automated order confirmations, delivery updates, promotional offers, loyalty rewards, and collect feedback after each order.\nProfessional Services\nAutomate consultation bookings, send reminders, share documents, follow up on leads, and provide instant responses to common queries.\nSports Equipment Brand\nHow Cosco, one of the most renowned Sporting equipment companies used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore conversions.\nExplore Case Study\nDonation Collection Platform\nDiscover how Give, India's most trusted donations collection platform used WhatsApp to achieve a\n90% Payment success rate\n&\n15X ROI\n.\nExplore Case Study\nEdtech Platform\nCheck out how PhysicsWallah, an Edtech giant used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore Leads through WhatsApp via AiSensy.\nExplore Case Study\nMultiple Human Live\nCha",
