      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\n98\n%\nOpen Rates\n45-\n60\n%\nClick Rates\n2.6\nBn+\nActive Users\n7\n%\nEngagement Rate\nImport contacts & broadcast unlimited WhatsApp messages\nImport an unlimited number of contacts and\nbroadcast pre-approved messages\ninstantly.\nPre-Approved Message Templates\nCreate your own Template Message and submit for approval ou use one of our pre-approved Template Messages from our library. Ensure compliance and avoid number blocking.\nAdvanced Audience Segmentation\nFilter contacts by tags, attributes, user behavior, and campaigns, enabling highly targeted messages for specific audiences.\nMessage Personalization\nCreate personalized messages based on user attributes like name, location, or behavior to boost engagement.\nCarousel Cards and Interactive Button Messages\nSend visually appealing messages with up to 10 images or videos, including actionable buttons to drive 60% more clicks.\nCampaign Scheduling\nSchedule your broadcasts up to two months in advance, optimizing delivery across different time zones.\nReal-Time Analytics\nTrack key metrics such as delivery rates, read rates, clicks, and responses, enabling quick and informed adjustments.\nRetargeting Campaigns\nRe-engage users based on past interactions, such as read messages, replies, or clicks on CTA buttons.\nComplete Automation and Integration\nSeamlessly integrate with CRMs, eCommerce platforms, and tools like Zapier, Shopify, and HubSpot to automate workflows and maximize results.\nLog in to Your AiSensy Dashboard\nSign in to your AiSensy account and make sure your WhatsApp Business API is fully approved and active. Without an active API, broadcast messaging will not be enabled.\nHow to Apply for WhatsApp Business API\nGo to the \"Contacts\" Section and Import Your Contacts\n•\nAccess the \"Contacts\" section in the AiSensy app.\n•\nUpload a list of opted-in contacts in CSV format or sync directly from your integrated tools.\n•\nUse tags and attributes to organize your audience for targeted broadcasts.\nCreate Your Campaign\n•\nGo to the \"Broadcast\" tab and click \"Create Campaign.\"\n•\nSelect a pre-approved WhatsApp message template or create a new one for approval.\n•\nPersonalize the message by adding variables like user names or custom fields to make it more engaging.\nLearn More\nSegment Your Audience\n•\nFilter your contacts by tags, attributes, or past interactions (e.g., read, replied, or clicked users).\n•\nSelect the most relevant audience to receive your broadcast.\nSchedule or Send Your Broadcast\n•\nChoose between sending your broadcast immediately or scheduling it for a later time.\n•\nLeverage AiSensy’s scheduling feature to plan messages up to 2 months in advance for optimal timing.\nMonitor Performance\n•\nGo to the \"Campaigns\" page to track your broadcast’s performance in real time.\n•\nAnalyze key metrics such as delivery rates, read rates, replies, and clicks.\n•\nUse this data to refine your strategy and improve future campaigns.\nLearn More\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Sup",
