      "summary": "AiSensy's WhatsApp Forms help you collect user inputs without any redirects. Capture high-intent leads and automate follow-ups instantly with Chatbots.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nTalk to Sales\nAPI integration\nReceive form information and automatically send it to your preferred CRM or management software. Automate time-consuming tasks effortlessly.\nCustomizable\nDesign flows tailored to your business needs, from simple FAQs to complex customer journeys.\nLearn More\nStreamline Lead Qualification & Data Collection\nGuide users through a well-designed flow to qualify leads and capture crucial information.\nThis allows you to effortlessly collect valuable user information without requiring real-time communication. It's a quick and efficient way to collect useful user information, making it ideal for businesses of all sizes.\nConduct Surveys & collect feedback directly within WhatsApp\nUse WhatsApp Forms to conduct surveys seamlessly. Collect feedback, preferences, or opinions from your audience.\nThis simplifies data collection and enables you to gather insights in a user-friendly way, directly through WhatsApp.\nSeamlessly process Loan Applications\nWhatsApp Forms is a great way to process loan applications, offering a smooth, user-friendly experience.\nFintech Businesses can use these forms to:\n✅Display pre-approved loan amounts with customisable terms like repayment periods.\n✅Allow users to choose disbursement and payment methods.\n✅Authenticate user identity for secure applications.\nThis use case is perfect for pre-approved loans, credit card offers, loan calculators, and more.\nSimplify Insurance sales\nBusinesses can create WhatsApp forms to:\n✅Collect user preferences (e.g., members covered, health risks, premium amounts).\n✅Offer personalised insurance quotes based on the user’s inputs.\n✅Enable users to customise and select their ideal plan.\nThis is an excellent way to enhance the user experience for insurance quotes, renewals, and onboarding processes.\nCollect Purchase Intent\nUnderstand what your customers want by using WhatsApp Forms to gather purchase intent.\nUsing WhatsApp forms, you can:\n✅Collect customer data, such as name and contact details.\n✅Allow users to indicate their interests in specific products or services.\nYou can use this data to create targeted sales campaigns and personalized promotions that resonate with your audience.\nDrive conversions with Personalized Offers\nHelp users reach purchase decision easily with tailored offers via WhatsApp Forms.\nLet users:\n✅Select products they’re interested in and specify their budget.\n✅Receive personalised recommendations on what to purchase.\n✅Get clear instructions on completing their purchase seamlessly.\nNot just for products, you can drive event ticket sales and boost conversions for your services.\nTalk to Sales\nPlacing Orders\nCollect product choices, quantities, and delivery preferences through the form. Integrate payment options for a smooth and complete shopping experience.\nEvent Registration\nDesign the form to capture attendee details, then confirm their registration and send event information directly via WhatsApp.\nBooking Appointments\nCustomize forms for yo",
