      "title": "WhatsApp Payments",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Transform your customer interactions by allowing payments directly through WhatsApp. Accept payments via UPI, net banking and cards.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nSend Payment messages via Live Chat &\nChatbot Flows\nNot only can you broadcast payment messages to all users, but you can also shoot payment messages to individual users directly from Live Chat & chatbot flows.\nTrack Payment Status &\nRetarget\nEffortlessly\nMonitor pending & successful payments in a campaign and further send retargeting campaigns to users who failed to complete the payment.\nVerify Payment status from\nUser Profile\nYou can easily verify the payment status of customers individually from the payments section under the user profile of a customer.\nView All Payments Received in One\nUnified Dashboard\nEnsure a seamless transition from automated chatbot interactions to live human support, maintaining conversation flow and customer satisfaction.\nWorks Seamlessly with\nRazorpay, PayU\nand others PGs.\nConnect your Payment Gateway to AiSensy and start collecting payment on WhatsApp.\nConvenience\nCustomers can complete transactions within their chat window, eliminating the need to switch platforms.\nSecurity\nPowered by WhatsApp’s encryption, ensuring every transaction is safe.\nEfficiency\nReduce payment friction and boost conversion rates by streamlining the payment process.\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Support on the same Whatsapp number.\nLearn More\nChatbot Flow\nBuilder\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nRetarget\nUsers on WhatsApp\nAiSensy’s WhatsApp Retarget feature allows you to segregate your audience and Re-Broadcast for higher conversions.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nScheduler\nSchedule Broadcasts up to 2 months ahead of time across varying timezones.\nLearn More\nImport, Broadcast &\nTrack\nTrack users clicking on your message's CTA buttons with this Pro Feature.\nLearn More\nAds that\nClick\nto WhatsApp\nDrive 5x More Leads with Ads that Click to WhatsApp.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nWebviews\nLoad web pages directly within WhatsApp. No more losing customers to external browsers.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nForms\nCreate and send forms with this native integration. Capture leads, book appointments, collect feedback, and more.\nLearn More\nSports Equipment Brand\nHow Cosco, one of the most renowned Sporting equipment companies used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore conversions.\nExplore Case Study\nDonation Collection Platform\nDiscover how Give, India's most trusted donations collection platform used WhatsApp to achieve a\n90% Payment success rate\n&\n15X ROI\n.\nExplore Case Study\nEdtech Platform\nCheck out how PhysicsWallah, an Edtech giant used AiSensy to drive\n3x\nmore Leads through WhatsApp via AiSensy.\nExplore Case Study\nStart for FREE\nBook a Demo\nIs WhatsApp Payments secure?\nYes, WhatsApp Payments uses end-to-end encryption to protect all transactions.\nWhat payment methods are supported?\nWhatsApp Payments supports major banks and payment gateways for ease of use.\nHow do I track payments?\nAll transactions can be tracked directly within your WhatsA",
