      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features/whatsapp-retargeting",
      "title": "WhatsApp Retargeting",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "AiSensy helps you run Smart WhatsApp retargeting campaigns that convert. Re-engage interested leads and drive more conversions.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nWhatsApp Broadcast Scheduler\nRemove the burden of manual messaging. AiSensy lets you schedule your WhatsApp Broadcasts, freeing up valuable time for your team to focus on strategy and growth. Say goodbye to repetitive tasks and hello to streamlined operations.\nTarget High-Interest Users\nNot all users are created equal—focus on those who matter. Retarget users who showed interest by reading, replying, or clicking the CTA button in your WhatsApp messages. By zeroing in on engaged users, you can triple your conversion rates and maximize the impact of your campaigns.\nEfficient Spending\nMaximize your marketing ROI by focusing on customers who have already shown interest in your products or services.\nHighly Personalized Communication\nSend messages that matter to your customers. Use customer data to craft personalized retargeting messages that resonate and prompt action.\nEnhanced Customer Insights\nKnowledge is power. AiSensy's real-time analytics provide deep insights into your customers' behavior. Understand who is engaging with your messages, and use this data to create even more effective retargeting campaigns.\nHot Leads\nUsers who replied or clicked in previous campaigns\nSerious Buyers\nUsers who viewed products or pricing but didn’t convert\nEngaged Readers\nUsers who opened messages but took no action\nCart Abandoners\nUsers who dropped off before completing checkout\nRepeat Buyers\nIdeal for upsell, cross-sell, and “you may also like” offers\nInactive Users\nRe-engage past customers and warm prospects\nSelect Your Audience & Create a Broadcast Campaign\nGo to Contacts Page 👉 Select the contacts you want to target with a WhatsApp Broadcast 👉 Click the Broadcast button.\nLearn More\nShoot a WhatsApp Broadcast\nAfter selecting your contacts, click the Broadcast button. Fill in the Campaign Name, choose from a pre-approved message template, and set the necessary parameters.\nFinally, hit 'Send Now' to dispatch your campaign.\nLearn More\nMonitor Campaign Analytics\nNavigate to the Campaigns Page and select your latest campaign to view its performance.\nHere, you'll see a comprehensive report on messages sent, delivered, read, replied to, and any failures.\nLearn More\nChoose the Audience you Wish to Retarget\nFilter your audience based on three key interactions:\nRead:\nUsers who have read your WhatsApp message.\nReplied:\nUsers who responded to your message.\nClicked:\nUsers who clicked on the CTA button in your message.\nBroadcast the WhatsApp Retarget Campaign\nFinally, send your retargeting message to these selected users on WhatsApp.\nTip:\nPersonalize your retargeting message to boost your conversion chances.\nLearn More\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Support on the same Whatsapp number.\nLearn More\nChatbot Flow\nBuilder\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nRetarget\nUsers on WhatsApp\nAiSensy’s WhatsApp Retarget feature allows you to se",
