      "forms": []
    },
    {
      "url": "https://aisensy.com/features/whatsapp-scheduler",
      "title": "WhatsApp Scheduler",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Plan your campaigns with AiSensy’s WhatsApp Scheduler. Automate message delivery, reduce manual work & reach your audience when it matters most.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\n98\n%\nOpen Rates\n45-\n60\n%\nClick Rates\n2.6\nBn+\nActive Users\n7\n%\nEngagement Rate\nSchedule Messages in Advance\nPlan your campaigns up to two months in advance and let AiSensy deliver them at the scheduled date and time, ensuring your messages reach your audience precisely when it matters most.\nReal-Time Analytics and Performance Tracking\nTrack key metrics such as delivery rates, read rates, clicks, and responses, helping you refine your strategy for better results.\nAutomate Personalized Broadcasts\nSend tailored messages to different customer segments, ensuring relevance and higher engagement.\nSet Up Recurring Campaigns\nSeamlessly integrate with CRMs, eCommerce platforms, and tools like Zapier, Shopify, and HubSpot to automate workflows and maximize results.\nSave Time and Resources\nAutomate your campaigns and free up your team to focus on other critical tasks.\nEnsure Timely Delivery of Messages\nSchedule messages to be sent at the optimal time, increasing the likelihood of engagement.\nImprove Engagement\nPersonalized and timely messages resonate better with customers, driving higher open rates and conversions.\nLog in or Create your AiSensy Account\nHead to\nwww.aisensy.com\nand click on \"Start For Free\" button.\nFill out the form with information details to create your account.\nLog in\nGo to the Contacts/ Campaigns page & create a Broadcast Campaign\nOn AiSensy dashboard, go to Contacts / Campaign Page and click \"+New\" to create a new campaign.\nHow to send a WhatsApp Broadcast with AiSensy\nSelect a pre-approved WhatsApp Template Message\nSelect one from your WhatsApp approved template messages.\nWhatsApp Template Message Guide\nEnable the 'Schedule Date & Time' option\nScroll down & enable the Schedule Date & Time option\nPick a suitable date, time & timezone to schedule the Broadcast\nSchedule campaign upto two months from today.\nClick 'Schedule Campaign'\nClick 'Schedule Campaign' to finish the scheduling process\nEdit or Cancel Scheduled Broadcasts\nYou can easily delete or reschedule your WhatsApp Broadcasts\nbefore they are sent:\nNavigate to the \"Campaigns\" section.\nLocate the scheduled message and select \"Edit\" or \"Cancel.\"\nMake the necessary changes or confirm the cancellation.\nThat’s it!\nGo to AiSensy App & schedule all your campaigns in advance.\nStart for FREE\nMultiple Human Live\nChat\nEnable Multiple Human-Agent Live Chat Support on the same Whatsapp number.\nLearn More\nChatbot Flow\nBuilder\nBuild multiple WhatsApp Chatbots easily, thanks to a drag-and-drop interface that requires zero coding expertise.\nLearn More\nRetarget\nUsers on WhatsApp\nAiSensy’s WhatsApp Retarget feature allows you to segregate your audience and Re-Broadcast for higher conversions.\nLearn More\nWhatsApp\nBroadcasts\nSchedule Broadcasts up to 2 months ahead of time across varying timezones.\nLearn More\nImport, Broadcast &\nTrack\nTrack users clicking on your message's CTA buttons with this Pro Feature.\nLearn More\nAds that\nClick\nto WhatsApp\nDrive 5x More Leads with Ads tha",
      "key_links": [],
