      "summary": "Increase customer satisfaction and minimize drop-offs with AiSensy’s WhatsApp Webviews. Open web pages directly in WhatsApp chats seamlessly",
      "content": "Talk to Sales\nWhy Most Businesses Lose Customers on WhatsApp\n(And How Webviews Fix It!)\nBrowser Redirections = Drop-offs\nEvery time a user is sent to an external website, chances are they'll dropoff due to slow loading webpage and many more reasons\nWhich causes\nLost Sales = Lost Revenue\nPotential customers abandon carts because of too many steps, leading to missed opportunities and decreased conversion rates.\nThe Solution\nWhatsApp Webviews\nKeep users engaged inside WhatsApp & get more\nsales\n,\nbookings\n, and\nsignups\neffortlessly.\nOpen Web within WhatsApp\nGive your users something new & exciting with Webviews\nEnhanced Engagement\nSimplify complex processes, like booking buses with hundreds of stops, directly within the chat, along with a ton of other unique use cases.\nIncreased Conversion Rates\nMinimize drop-offs and maximize customer satisfaction.\nTalk to Sales\nEnhanced User Experience\nBy keeping the process within\nWhatsApp\n, users enjoy a much better & faster experience, improving engagement and conversions.\nIncreased Conversion Rates\nYou minimise drop-offs and boost\nconversions\nby enabling customers to complete actions like purchases or bookings directly within WhatsApp.\nStreamlined Customer Support\nHandle\norder tracking\n, issue resolution, and real-time conversations all within the WhatsApp interface, leading to faster responses and happier customers.\nPersonalized Interactions\nDeliver tailored content and offers within the chat, enhancing\nuser engagement\nand loyalty.\nSimplified Data Collection\nGather customer information seamlessly through\nforms\nor surveys within WhatsApp, making data collection more efficient.\nEnhanced Security & Trust\nLeverage WhatsApp's secure environment to build\ntrust\nwith customers while maintaining end-to-end encryption for all interactions.\nE-commerce\nCustomers can view and add products from multiple options and make purchases directly in WhatsApp without the restrictions of