    {
      "url": "https://aisensy.com/industries/automobile",
      "title": "Automobile",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Enhance sales leads, automate service reminders, and provide 24/7 assistance with AiSensy’s WhatsApp Business solutions tailored for the Automobile sector.",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nBuild no-code Chatbot in minutes\nBuild your Own Chatbot Flows your Way! Easy-to-use Chatbot & Catalog Flow builder to build your conversational journeys.\nBroadcast Offers to Unlimited Contacts\nBroadcast personalized offers to unlimited users in one go - without getting your Number blocked!\nImport, Broadcast, Track Results and Retarget\n3x your conversions by sending Retargeting Campaigns to the most relevant audience group.\nAnswer customer queries with 1:1 Live Chat\nEnable Chatbot Flows or have multiple team members to provide seamless Live Chat support on a single WhatsApp Business number.\nLead Generation & Test Drive Bookings\nCar dealerships can use WhatsApp to automate lead generation and test drive scheduling.\nCustomers can inquire about specific models and book test drives directly through WhatsApp, providing a seamless and efficient process.\nService Reminders & Maintenance Alerts\nAutomate service reminders for routine vehicle maintenance, oil changes, and inspections.\nDealerships can notify customers of upcoming services, ensuring vehicles are maintained on time and improving customer retention.\nBoost sales with Timely Offers and Announcements\nPromote new models, seasonal offers, or exclusive discounts directly to customers through WhatsApp.\nBy leveraging AiSensy’s platform, dealerships can deliver compelling conversational flows with interactive CTAs, dynamic product lists, rich media and more.\n24/7 Customer Support with WhatsApp Chatbots\nAiSensy’s smart WhatsApp Chatbots allow you to offer real-time customer support for queries on pricing, vehicle availability, and service bookings.\nFor more complex issues, seamlessly transfer conversations to live agents, ensuring customers receive timely, accurate information at all times.\nOrder Updates & Delivery Notifications\nKeep customers informed about the status of their vehicle orders.\nWhatsApp can be used to send real-time updates on order processing, expected delivery dates, and the readiness of their vehicle for pickup or delivery.\nPost-Purchase Follow-ups & Feedback Collection\nAfter a purchase, use WhatsApp to follow up with customers, collect feedback, and schedule future maintenance services.\nThis helps maintain a long-term relationship with the customer, improving satisfaction and encouraging repeat business.\n98\n%\nOpen Rates\n45-\n60\n%\nClick Rates\n2.6\nBn+\nActive Users\n7\n%\nEngagement Rate\nEducation & Edtech\nEngage students, automate inquiries, and simplify admissions. Explore how WhatsApp can revolutionize your edtech communication.\nExplore Use Case\nBanking & Fintech\nEnhance customer service, streamline KYC, and much more. Discover how WhatsApp can revolutionize your banking and fintech operations.\nExplore Use Case\nHealthcare\nSchedule appointments, share health tips, and provide personalized patient care. Explore how WhatsApp can elevate your healthcare communication\nExplore Use Case\nEvents & Webinar\nBoost registrations, send reminders, and gather feedback effortless",
