      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nBuild no-code Chatbot in minutes\nBuild your Own Chatbot Flows your Way! Easy-to-use Chatbot & Catalog Flow builder to build your conversational journeys.\nBroadcast Offers to Unlimited Contacts\nBroadcast personalized offers to unlimited users in one go - without getting your Number blocked!\nImport, Broadcast, Track Results and Retarget\n3x your conversions by sending Retargeting Campaigns to the most relevant audience group.\nAnswer customer queries with 1:1 Live Chat\nEnable Chatbot Flows or have multiple team members to provide seamless Live Chat support on a single WhatsApp Business number.\nFlight Booking Confirmation & Real‑Time Status Updates\nAutomatically send travelers a branded WhatsApp message immediately after flight purchase that confirms booking details (PNR, departure/arrival times) and provides real‑time status alerts (delays, gate changes).\nLearn More\nHotel Reservation Confirmation\nConfirm guests’ hotel bookings via WhatsApp immediately after payment, detailing check‑in/out dates, room type and booking reference.\nExclusive Upsell Offers\nIncrease revenue by targeting hotel guests with special offers, such as:\nSpa deals\nRooftop dining experience\nLate checkout upgrade\nLuxurious in-room breakfast\nLimited-Time Vacation Offer WhatsApp Message\nCreate urgency & drive 3x more package bookings for your Travel Agency with WhatsApp.\nCheck Template Library\n24/7 Customer Support\nAiSensy’s smart WhatsApp Chatbots allow you to offer real-time customer support for queries on pricing, availability, and service bookings.\nFor more complex issues, seamlessly transfer conversations to live agents, ensuring customers receive timely and human support.\nLearn More\nVacation Discount Offer WhatsApp Message\nDrive 3x more package Bookings for your Travel Agency with this WhatsApp Template.\nExplore Templates\nLimited-Time Vacation Offer WhatsApp Message\nCreate urgency & drive 3x more package Bookings for your Travel Agency with this WhatsApp Template.\nExplore Templates\nFlight Delayed WhatsApp Message\nAutomate flight delay updates using this\nWhatsApp API-powered notification template\n.\nExplore Templates\nHotel Booking Offer WhatsApp Message\nIncrease direct hotel bookings with this\nspecial offer message for travelers\n.\nExplore Templates\nFlight Boarding WhatsApp Message\nAutomate updates for flight boarding with this WhatsApp Template.\nExplore Templates\nHotel Booking Confirmation WhatsApp Message\nSend automated booking confirmations for hotels, ensuring a\nseamless guest experience\n.\nExplore Templates\nTravel Newsletter WhatsApp Message\nBoost engagement for your\ntravel and tourism newsletter\nby sending updates via WhatsApp.\nExplore Templates\nHotel Alerts WhatsApp Message\nKeep travelers informed by\nautomating important hotel alerts\n, such as check-in times and room upgrades.\nExplore Templates\nHotel Payment Confirmation Message\nSend instant payment confirmations for\nhotel bookings and tour packages\nvia WhatsApp API.\nExplore Templates\nFlight Status W",
