cates, and other critical documents\nto patients via WhatsApp.\nThis eliminates the need for physical visits just to collect reports, ensuring faster access to crucial health information while maintaining data privacy and security.\nSchedule a Call Now\nAllow students to access & download educational materials within WhatsApp\nEnable citizens to\ntrack government-related shipments, postal deliveries, and official documents\nin real time through WhatsApp.\nWhether it’s an important legal paper, a government-issued ID, or a subsidy-related parcel, users can simply send a message and get instant tracking updates—reducing uncertainty and follow-up calls.\nSchedule a Call Now\nAllow citizens to track shipments & courier within WhatsApp\nEnable citizens to\ntrack government-related shipments, postal deliveries, and official documents\nin real time through WhatsApp.\nWhether it’s an important legal paper, a government-issued ID, or a subsidy-related parcel, users can simply send a message and get instant tracking updates—reducing uncertainty and follow-up calls.\nSchedule a ",
