      "title": "Shopify",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Seamlessly connect your Shopify app with AiSensy and automate notifications for order, delivery, feedback & more on WhatsApp!",
      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\nRecover Abandoned Carts\nAutomate personalized WhatsApp reminders to customers who left items in their cart to complete their purchase.\nOrder Confirmation & Updates\nProvide instant order confirmations, shipping updates, and delivery notifications via WhatsApp\nReduce RTO (Return to Origin)\nConfirm COD orders and cut down on returns with WhatsApp notifications.\nFeedback Collection & Reviews\nGather valuable insights to improve your products and services.\nTimely Reorder Reminders\nBoost repeat purchases by proactively reminding customers to restock their favorite products.\nPromotional Campaigns & Offers\nLaunch promotions, send offers, and drive engagement directly through WhatsApp.\nCopy Your Shopify App Token\n• In your AiSensy app, go to Ecomm+ -> Shopify Store Setup.\n• Tap Copy Shopify App token (you'll need this in a bit).\n• Now tap Install app.\nHead to the Shopify App Store\n• Clicking the Install app button will take you straight to the AiSensy app in the Shopify App Store.\n• Tap the Install button there.\nConfirm the installation\nOn the next screen, tap Install again to confirm.\nPay a Small Setup Fee\nComplete the one-time payment of $1 to proceed.\n(If you prefer not to pay, check out the steps to connect manually at the link provided below)\n.\nPaste the token into AiSensy and Connect\nReturn to the AiSensy app, paste the Shopify token you copied and click Connect.\nIn AiSensy app, refresh your screen and voila! Magic Done!\nYour Shopify store is now connected to AiSensy in just a few simple steps.\nNote: If you don't wish to spend the $1 setup fee, follow the steps in the link below.\nHow to Manually Connect your Shopify Store\nAbandoned Cart Reminder\nHi {{Customer Name}} 👋\nYou left something behind in your cart!\n🛍️\n{{Product Name}}\n💰\n{{Price}}\nComplete your purchase here before it goes out of stock:\n👉 {{Checkout Link}}\nOrder Confirmation\nHi {{Customer Name}} 🎉\nThank you for your order! We’ve successfully received your purchase.\n🧾\nOrder ID:\n{{Order ID}}\n📦\nItems:\n{{Product Names}}\nWe’ll notify you as soon as your order is shipped.\nShipping Update\nGreat news, {{Customer Name}} 🚚\nYour order\n{{Order ID}}\nhas been shipped!\n🔗 Track your order here: {{Tracking Link}}\nNeed help? Just reply to this message — we’re here for you!\nCOD Order Confirmation\nHi {{Customer Name}},\nPlease confirm your\nCash on Delivery\norder for\n{{Product Name}}\n.\n👉 Reply\nYES\nto confirm\n👉 Reply\nNO\nto cancel\nThis helps us deliver your order faster 🚀\nPost-Delivery Feedback Request\nHi {{Customer Name}} 😊\nYour order has been delivered! We’d love to know how your experience was.\n⭐ Rate your purchase here: {{Review Link}}\nYour feedback helps us serve you better.\nReorder / Upsell Message\nHi {{Customer Name}} 👋\nRunning lowne low on\n{{Previously Purchased Product}}\n?\nReorder in just one click:\n👉 {{Product Link}}\n🎁 Enjoy an exclusive offer just for you!\nPromotional Campaign Message\n🔥 Limited-Time Offer!\nGet\n{{Discount}}% OFF\non our best-selling products.\n🛍️ Shop now: {{Store ",
