      "url": "https://aisensy.com/pricing",
      "title": "Pricing",
      "page_type": "pricing",
      "summary": "WhatsApp Business API Pricing in India for AiSensy Platform. Starts at ₹1500/month. Affordable Pricing for the Best WhatsApp Marketing Platform in India",
      "content": "AiSensy WhatsApp Business API pricing (India). Plans, all with unlimited team members: Free Forever (₹0); Basic ₹1,500/month; Pro ₹3,200/month (most popular); Premium ₹9,100/month; Unlimited ₹45,000/month; Enterprise is custom-priced. There is NO setup fee and AiSensy does not charge to procure the WhatsApp Business API. Meta's per-message template charges are billed separately on top: Marketing ₹1.09, Utility and Authentication ₹0.145, and Service messages are free within the 24-hour customer service window. Pro adds over Basic: campaign scheduling, click tracking, budget & analytics, and project APIs. AI Chatbots & AI Agents are add-ons (Basic ₹2,500/month, Pro+AI ₹3,500/month). A 14-day free trial is available. \nMonthly\nQuarterly\nSAVE 5%\nYearly\nSAVE 10%\nCompare Plans\nAll billing is pre-paid. WhatsApp Conversation Credits are recharged & managed separately (Marketing ₹1.09, Utility & Authentication ₹0.145 per message for Indian users; Service conversations are always free).\n Need help choosing?\nTalk to our team →\nCompare Plans\nPlans + Chatbot & AI add-ons\n✕\nAdd-ons\n· Chatbots & AI Agents, charged separately on top of any plan\nFree Forever plan is shown in the cards. \"Unlimited\" limits follow AiSensy's fair-use policy (Agents up to 200, Tags up to 500, Attributes up to 100). Enterprise limits are tailored to your scale.\nExplore International Pricing\nExplore Pricing\nExplore Pricing\n₹2000\n+ GST Per Year\nBuy Now\n₹299\nQuarterly (For 3 months)\nBuy Now\nIndian Virtual Number\nBuy Indian Virtual Number for WhatsApp Business API (Requires GST/ MSME for KYC)\nIndian Number (Eg. +9186XXXX1234, +9186XXXX7891)\nNo Need to maintain SIM Card\nUse this Number to get WhatsApp Business API via AiSensy\nFree Onboarding Call\nBasic\nKeyword Chatbots\nSolid for structured, predictable use cases.\n₹2,500\n/\nMonth\n5 keyword-based chatbots\nDrag-and-drop flow builder\nWhatsApp Cart Management\nShare Catalogs & Products on WhatsApp\nIntegrated