      "url": "https://aisensy.com/products/showroom-kit",
      "title": "Showroom Kit",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Start WhatsApp marketing with official WhatsApp API on your mobile, starting at just ₹500 with AiSensy Automations Lite Plan + Qr Kit.",
      "content": "Your Official — Meta BSP\nTurn\nWalk-In Customers\ninto\nRepeat Sales\nwith\nWhatsApp Marketing\nCapture every customer and bring them back automatically on WhatsApp via\nAiSensy Automation Lite Plan + QR Kit\n🎁 Includes FREE QR Kit worth ₹500\nStart at just ₹500/month →\nPowered by Official WhatsApp API\nRun WhatsApp Marketing safely without risking your number getting blocked.\nSee All Your Customers in One Place\nEvery customer who scans your QR is saved automatically — all in one list\nSend Bulk WhatsApp Campaigns in Seconds\nRun offers, new stock alerts, and festival sales by messaging all customers in one click.\nReply to Customers Anytime from Your Phone\nStay connected and respond instantly on WhatsApp — from anywhere.\nTrack Campaign Performance & Responses\nSee what’s working, who’s responding, and what drives repeat sales.\nMonitor Customer Growth from QR Scans\nTrack how many walk-in customers you’re capturing every day.\nWatch 60-sec Demo\nStart Bringing Customers Back →\nNever Lose any Walk-in Customer\nEvery customer who scans gets saved automatically\nIncrease Sales Without You Following Up with Customers\nMessages are sent automatically to their WhatsApp after every visit\nAutomated Drip Sequences That Bring Customers Back\nFrom welcome offers to reminders and updates, customers receive a timed sequence of WhatsApp messages that nudge them to return and make purchase.\nSend Bulk WhatsApp Campaigns to All Your Customers\nRun sales, offers, and announcements in one click by messaging your entire customer base directly on WhatsApp without getting blocked.\nSimple to Use. No Technical Knowledge Needed\nEverything works from your phone\nSend offers and updates\nShare festive offers, discounts, or new arrivals when you want customers to visit again.\nSend reminders\nRemind customers about their next visit, service, or refill at the right time.\nAnswer questions anytime\nReply when customers ask about prices, availability, or timings.\nConfirm bookings and appointments\nSend confirmations so customers know exactly when to come.\nCollect feedback privately\nAsk how their visit went and fix issues before they turn into public reviews.\n‹\n›\nPlace QR Stand. The beginning of WhatsApp Marketing for your store\nWalk-in customers scan your QR and send “Hi” on WhatsApp\nTheir name & number get saved automatically\n👉 100+ new contacts/month on average\nImport Your Existing Customers on Your WhatsApp\nAlready have numbers in your phone or Excel?\nUpload them in one click and start messaging\n👉 500+ contacts added instantly\nSend Offers to Everyone (Without Getting Blocked)\nSend offers, reminders, and updates to all customers\nUsing the official WhatsApp API\n👉 Up to 10x ROI from repeat customers\n₹500\n👉\nPer Month (GST Included)\nCancel anytime • 4–7 days delivery\nGet QR Kit + Start Now\n$79\nPer Month, Billed Annually\nBuy Now\nAiSensy Automation Lite Plan + FREE QR Kit\nEverything you need to\ncapture walk-in customers\nand bring them back using\nWhatsApp Marketing\n1 extra customer per week = full recovery of ",
