      "content": "Start for FREE\nBook a Demo\n🛍️ WhatsApp Verification for\nE-commerce\nInstantly boost customer trust and increase conversions by clearly showcasing your authenticity.\n💳 WhatsApp Verification for\nFinancial Services\nClearly differentiate your legitimate financial brand and build stronger customer confidence.\n📚 WhatsApp Verification for\nEducational Institutions\nGain trust faster with students and parents, increasing engagement in admissions and courses.\n🩺 WhatsApp Verification for\nHealthcare Providers\nInstantly assure patients of your authenticity and improve communication efficiency.\n🏨 WhatsApp Verification for\nTravel Agencies\nInstantly build credibility for bookings and drive greater customer engagement.\n🎯 WhatsApp Verification for\nMarketing Agencies\nClearly highlight your professionalism to attract more clients and improve interactions.\n🎬 WhatsApp Verification for\nEntertainment Services\nEnhance audience engagement and ensure your content reaches fans safely and authentically.\n🎉 WhatsApp Verification for\nEvent Planning Services\nBuild client trust by showcasing your verified status, leading to more bookings and satisfaction.\n🏢 WhatsApp Verification for\nOther Businesses\nDon’t see your industry listed here? No worries. Connect with our Live Chat Support team and they’ll assist you.\nWhatsApp API Setup\nYour business must be live & active on WhatsApp Business API!\nComplete Facebook Business / KYC Verification\nYou must complete the Meta business verification or KYC Verification process on your Meta Business Manager account.\n5 Organic PR/ News Article\nYou must have at least 5 organic PR/ news articles published for your brand online.\nNote\n: Paid PR doesn't count!\nTier 2 or Above Messaging Level\nYour account must be in Tier 2 or above messaging level. While Tier 1 may also apply, you must have exchanged 10-15 messages first.\n2FA Verification\nTurn on 2-step verification to apply for official WhatsApp Blue tick\nNotable and Reputable Business\nYour business must be a notable and reputable business.\nRegistered Business\nOnly registered businesses are eligible — individuals are not allowed.\nApproved Display Name\nYour Display Name must be approved by Meta.\nHigh-quality WABA\nThe account should be actively engaged in high-quality messaging.\nGo to the AiSensy Dashboard\nGo to the AiSensy Dashboard & apply for WhatsApp Business API.\nAn approved WhatsApp Business API account is necessary to apply for Green Tick Verification.\nGo to Dashboard\nClick the \"Apply for Blue Tick\" Button\nGo to the Dashboard & locate \"\nApply for Blue Tick\n\" button shown in the image below.\nClick the Button which will redirect you to WhatsApp.\nFill out the Blue Tick Application Form\nOn the next screen, the Green Tick form will pop up which you need to fill very carefully to apply for the WhatsApp Green Tick. Once you fill out the form, we'll apply for your WhatsApp Green Tick by sharing your details with Meta.\nYou will receive a response to your application directly from Meta in the next 7-10 days.\nG",
      "key_links": [],
      "forms": []
    },
    {
      "url": "https://aisensy.com/products/whatsapp-marketing",
      "title": "WhatsApp Marketing",
      "page_type": "product",
      "summary": "Tap into the power of WhatsApp Marketing with AiSensy. Official WhatsApp Marketing Software to send broadcasts, automate chats & grow revenue. Start for FREE today.",
      "content": "Try AiSensy FREE for 14 Days\nBook a Demo\nLearn More\n98\n%\nOpen Rates\n45-\n60\n%\nClick Rates\n2.6\nBn+\nActive Users\n7\n%\nEngagement Rate\nImport &\nBroadcast\nWhatsApp messages Instantly\nSend WhatsApp Campaigns to all your contacts in seconds without getting blocked.\nCollect\nPayments\nOn WhatsApp\nYes, collect payments seamlessly on WhatsApp via WhatsApp Pay, UPI, Net banking and cards.\nRun\nClick to WhatsApp Ads\nCreate ads that land directly to WhatsApp, capture leads instantly, and boost conversions.\nSee 3-5X more leads & slash your cost per lead.\nBuild\nNo-code\nWhatsApp Chatbots\nin Minutes\nBuild no-code WhatsApp chatbots that drive sales, answer up to 85% queries effectively and qualify leads while you sleep.\nSend\nAutomated\nCTA Based Notifications on WhatsApp\nTrigger automated WhatsApp messages for abandoned carts, order updates, or exclusive offers. Connect your CRM or eCommerce store like Shopify, WooCommerce, Hubspot & more\nGet the Official WhatsApp\nBlue Tick Verification\nBuild instant trust and credibility with the verified Blue Tick badge on your WhatsApp Business profile. Show customers you’re an authentic brand and increase message open rates and engagement.\nTrack\nCampaign Performance\nwith Advanced Analytics\nMeasure WhatsApp message delivery, reads, clicks, conversions, and revenue from one dashboard to optimize every WhatsApp campaign with data-backed insights.\nIntegrates Seamlessly with Your\nTech Stack\nConnect AiSensy with tools like Shopify, Zoho, HubSpot, and Google Sheets to keep your workflows unified and data in sync.\nAnswer customer queries with\n1:1 Live Chat\nEnable Chatbot Flows or have multiple team members to provide seamless Live Chat support on a single WhatsApp Business number.\nBuild Quality Opt-In Lists\nOnly message users who have explicitly opted in. This ensures compliance, higher engagement, and reduces block rates.\nSegment Your Audience\nDivide your contacts by interest, purchase history, or demographics. Send targeted messages for higher relevance and conversion rates.\nPersonalize Your Messages\nUse customer names, purchase history, and preferences in your messages. Personal touch increases engagement and trust.\nSend at Optimal Times\nTest different times and days to find when your audience is most active. AiSensy analytics help identify the best sending windows.\nKeep Content Valuable & Short\nWhatsApp users prefer concise, actionable messages. Focus on value - offers, tips, or solutions - not just promotions.\nUse Clear Call-to-Actions\nInclude specific CTAs like \"Shop Now,\" \"Book a Demo,\" or \"Reply to Order.\" Make it easy for customers to take action.\nImproved Sales\nWhatsApp offers 5x more open rate & 10x more click-rates than Emails & SMS & helps 3x your sales\nImproves relations & Connectivity\nWhatsApp adds a personal touch to your conversations with personalized messages and real-time live chat.\nBuild Trust, Boost Authenticity\nBuild trust, show authenticity, and stand out with the WhatsApp Green Tick\nBoost Customer Satisfaction\n90% ",
